					<description><![CDATA[<p>Automatic deodorant filling machine Npack deodorant filling machine is one type of filling equipement, which adapts with advance hot filling technology,the working process is typically hot-fill,the solid formula is melted, then dispensed into the empty stick barrel, after filling,a cooling station(cooling tunnel) solidifies it before capping. Precise volume control is usually achieved with a piston [&#8230;]</p>
<p>El puesto <a href="https://www.npackpm.com/es/maquina-llenadora-de-desodorantes">Máquina llenadora de desodorantes</a> apareció por primera vez en <a href="https://www.npackpm.com/es">China Fabricante líder de máquinas llenadoras de líquidos</a>.</p>]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<div data-elementor-type="wp-page" data-elementor-id="5336" class="elementor elementor-5336" data-elementor-post-type="page">
